OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'Prisons are full, we can't
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftake any more'             
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The head of the Scottish Prison Service
OL,6, has said the jails are too full and she
OL,7, may soon have to say "enough is enough,
OL,8, we cannot take any more".              
OL,10,FTeresa Medhurst told BBC Disclosure    
OL,11,Fprisons were reaching a "tipping point"
OL,12,Fand emergency powers could be needed to
OL,13,Frelease inmates early.                 
OL,15,FShe said if numbers continued to rise, 
OL,16,Fdrastic measures could be needed as    
OL,17,Fsoon as next month.                    
OL,19,FThe prison boss said "all options would
OL,20,Fneed to be on the table".              
